title: League Wont Load (Mac)
body: i need some help with my league of legends application. When ever i try to load the game it won't let me, it loads up the icon in the menu bar and then closes and doesn't open. Ive tried replacing the userkemal as it says that that is the problem, but I'm not sure if that is correct or not. I've had this problem since october and I'm not sure what to do know. Please respond and help me.
